high_descs: Turn right for one step; turn left for one step to face the dresser.
Pick up the red pen from the dresser on the right.
Stand up holding the pen.
Put the pen in the black mug at the back of the dresser to the right.
Pick up the mug with the pen still inside.
Turn around and then right and walk to the door, turn left and take nine steps, turn right for one step and then left and stop.
Place the cup on the bottom right of the nightstand, to the right of the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put a black mug, with a red pen in it, on the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn right then face the table to your left.
Take the red pencil off of the table in front of you.
Face the cup on the table in front of you.
Place the red pencil in the cup on the table in front of you.
Take the cup off of the table in front of you.
Turn around and face your bed side table in front of you.
Place the cup with the pencil on the bed side table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place pencil on bed side table.

high_descs: Turn right, step forward, then turn left to be center with the desk.
Pick up the pencil on the right side in front of the cup.
Step forward to be closer to the desk.
Place the pencil inside the cup on the top right.
Pick up the cup from the desk.
Turn around and walk to the nightstand to the right side of the bed.
Place the cup on the lower right edge of the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a pencil inside a cup and place the cup on the nightstand.
